Author:

This is the application page for Vaadin. Switching navigation options just loads a different "page" or View onto the body area. Extends Vaadin UI class.

addNewMenuItem

public void addNewMenuItem(java.lang.String viewName,
                           java.lang.String viewLabel,
                           com.vaadin.navigator.View viewObj)
Adds a new View to the Navigator and adds a new menu option to the Header's menu bar. The default View should have a viewName set as "". New Views and menu options should be added in the init method

Parameters:
viewName - String view name, needs to be unique
viewLabel - String label to appear on the menu button
viewObj - View object corresponding to the menu option
